{
  "stem": "964.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But for the average Jewish people in Poland, poor people, they had nowhere to go, not a prayer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "19 years.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in, in 1939 Kalisz-- when the Germans invaded Poland-- this was on a Friday-- Saturday afternoon we had to really leave the town because the Germans were already about 5, 3 kilometers away from town.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew what we had to expect from the Poles-- Poles and Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when Poland was, was born, after World War I, Poland got a, a part of Germany in-- in-- incorporated into Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had quite a big population of Germans living in Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Poles we knew, we knew then what to expect from them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we, we got-- prepared ourselves to leave-- to leave town, to run away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, you know, we, we, we knew already the Poles antisemites.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans, what we knew from the-- from what we were taught, from witnesses that came in from-- away from Germany-- so we couldn't expect any-- anything good from them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we start running away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we left town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But this I have to tell you, we had a rabbi there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So people went-- you know, usually the rabbi is the wise man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He give you good advice and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People run to him, went to him and asked, rabbi, what should we do?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Should we run, or should we stay?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, no, you go home, stay, and God will help you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was in, in, in, in July-- no, in September, I think the war started.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, a Jew can only do things after he see the first star.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then he can do things, pack or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this, this was 5, 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans were already coming into town.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
